works.description: At £220,000 (or about $360,150), this yellow Lamborghini Asus VX3 laptop with black leather and yellow stitching seems simply outrageous, but considering the fact that it’s accompanied with a brand new Lamborghini Tag Heuer Meridist phone number 0136 of 1963 and a 2008 Lamborghini LP640 Roadster sports car, it’s worth the price. The three-year-old laptop comes with a 2.5 GHz processor, 4GB RAM, a leather keyboard cover and a yellow Lamborghini paint job.
